channel.description:
Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details.
Any help at all would be appreciated.
Also, when I run the server it says it is starting on 0.0.0.0:43594. I know 43594 is the port but 0.0.0.0 as an ip? Can I fix that and actually have it let me play?
Thanks.
EDIT:: I do have Hamachi.
